data.description: Nestled among the wooded landscape of Emerald Hills, this home is clean and move-in ready! The private setting of the property offers gorgeous views off of the front deck or city views atop the nearly 1.5 acre hill behind the home. Bring your chickens and utilize the large coop in the backyard! Inside, a kitchen and dining backs up to the hill with a large deck that can accommodate a hot tub.  The master suite, complete with gas fireplace, will certainly make a cozy space while the large bathroom and soaking tub create your own relaxing retreat. Two guest bedrooms and a guest bath are on the main floor, while the 4th bedroom and 3rd bath are located in the walk-out basement. The property is on septic and has two 2,200 gallon cisterns. Propane tank is owned.
